---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - AIToolGuide">
  <div class="legal-page">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container">
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="/" class="logo">
            <span class="logo-icon">💰</span>
            <span class="logo-text">AIToolGuide</span>
          </a>
          <div class="nav-actions">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="legal-content">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 26, 2026</p>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing or using AIToolGuide, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p>AIToolGuide provides information and tutorials about AI tools and their monetization potential. We do not guarantee any specific earnings or results from using the tools or methods described on our platform.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>3. User Accounts</h2>
          <h3>3.1 Registration</h3>
          <p>To access certain features, you must create an account. You agree to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
            <li>Maintain the security of your password</li>
            <li>Accept responsibility for all activities under your account</li>
            <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>3.2 Account Termination</h3>
          <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms or engage in fraudulent activity.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>4. User Content</h2>
          <p>By submitting content (success stories, comments, etc.), you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Grant us a non-exclusive license to use, modify, and display your content</li>
            <li>Represent that you own or have rights to the content</li>
            <li>Agree not to submit false or misleading information</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>5. Prohibited Activities</h2>
          <p>You may not:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Use our services for illegal purposes</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
            <li>Interfere with other users' access</li>
            <li>Upload malware or harmful code</li>
            <li>Scrape or automate access to our content</li>
            <li>Impersonate others</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>All content on AIToolGuide, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is our property or licensed to us. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without permission.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>Our services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Specific earnings or income results</li>
            <li>Accuracy of third-party tool information</li>
            <li>Uninterrupted or error-free service</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>9. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>10. Contact Information</h2>
          <p>For questions about these Terms, contact us at:</p>
          <p><a href="mailto:legal@ai2424.com">legal@ai2424.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .legal-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #0f172a 100%);
    }

    .header {
      padding: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
    }

    .logo-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .logo-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .back-link {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .legal-content {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      color: white;
    }

    .legal-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .last-updated {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .legal-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #667eea;
    }

    .legal-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0 12px;
    }

    .legal-section p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .legal-section ul {
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .legal-section li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .legal-section a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .legal-section a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .legal-content h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
